#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn12.37"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.37:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.37:0.2"
msgid "4. Kaḷārakhattiyavagga "
msgstr "4. Kaḷāra the Aristocrat "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.37:0.3"
msgid "37. Natumhasutta "
msgstr "37. Not Yours "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.65, sc1
msgctxt "sn12.37:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.37:1.2"
msgid "“Nāyaṃ, bhikkhave, kāyo tumhākaṃ napi aññesaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, this body doesn’t belong to you or to anyone else. "

msgctxt "sn12.37:1.3"
msgid "Purāṇamidaṃ, bhikkhave, kammaṃ abhisaṅkhataṃ abhisañcetayitaṃ vedaniyaṃ daṭṭhabbaṃ. "
msgstr "It’s old deeds, and should be seen as produced by choices and intentions, as something to be felt. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn12.37:2.1"
msgid "Tatra kho, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako paṭiccasamuppādaññeva sādhukaṃ yoniso manasi karoti: "
msgstr "A learned noble disciple carefully and properly attends to dependent origination itself: "

msgctxt "sn12.37:2.2"
msgid "‘iti imasmiṃ sati idaṃ hoti, imassuppādā idaṃ uppajjati; "
msgstr "‘When this exists, that is; due to the arising of this, that arises. "

msgctxt "sn12.37:2.3"
msgid "imasmiṃ asati idaṃ na hoti, imassa nirodhā idaṃ nirujjhati, yadidaṃ—"
msgstr "When this doesn’t exist, that is not; due to the cessation of this, that ceases. That is: "

msgctxt "sn12.37:2.4"
msgid "avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā; "
msgstr "Ignorance is a condition for choices. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.37:2.5"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "Choices are a condition for consciousness. … "

msgctxt "sn12.37:2.6"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti. "
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates. "

msgctxt "sn12.37:2.7"
msgid "Avijjāya tveva asesavirāganirodhā saṅkhāranirodho; "
msgstr "When ignorance fades away and ceases with nothing left over, choices cease. "

msgctxt "sn12.37:2.8"
msgid "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho … pe … "
msgstr "When choices cease, consciousness ceases. … "

msgctxt "sn12.37:2.9"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī’”ti. "
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.37:2.10"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
